Imports PROCESSING

1. User navigates to imports list view
2. Creates import
3. Fills in primary fields
4. saves
5. Staged Inventory imports section appears
6. User fills adds rows to the staged import rows. 
7. Once shipment arrives. Users activate the worker from the import record view to import all or individual rows to the inventory. 
8. Once all rows are imported the import is marked complete and inventory rows are useable


Rules
- Use a staged inventory import rows
- Worker copies those rows to inventory and uses correct fields. 